info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 15 at 7:11PM PST until January 16 at 7:00AM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 AM PST MONDAY... * WHAT...South to southwest winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph expected. * WHERE...The mountains of San Luis Obispo and Santa Barbara Counties. * WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 7 AM PST Monday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
